---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'May 14, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | alot.capital"
  description="Terms governing use of the alot.capital website, operated by A Lot of Land LLC."
>
  <section class="section bg-bg-dark !pt-12 md:!pt-20">
    <div class="container-narrow max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white leading-tight mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-white/85 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">1. Agreement</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using alot.capital (the "Site"), operated by A Lot of Land LLC ("we", "us"), you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">2. Not an offer or solicitation</h2>
          <p>
            The Site is provided for general information only. Nothing on the Site constitutes an offer to sell, a solicitation to buy, or a recommendation of any security or investment. Any actual investment opportunity is offered only through separate written agreements, applicable disclosures, and only to persons who qualify under applicable law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">3. No advice</h2>
          <p>
            Content on the Site is educational and general in nature. It is not investment, legal, tax, or accounting advice. You should consult your own licensed advisors before making any investment decision.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">4. Risk of loss</h2>
          <p>
            Real estate and land investments involve substantial risk, including partial or total loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results. No return is guaranteed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">5. Your submissions</h2>
          <p>
            When you submit information through a form on the Site (the free guide request, the investor application, or the chat widget), you represent that the information is accurate, that you are at least 18 years of age, and that you have the right to provide it. You consent to our use of that information as described in our <a href="/privacy" class="text-gold hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">6. Messaging consent</h2>
          <p>
            If you opt in via the chat widget, you authorize A Lot of Land LLC to send SMS/text messages and place calls to the number you provide, using automated means, for follow-up related to your inquiry. Standard message and data rates may apply. Consent is not a condition of any purchase or investment. You may opt out at any time by replying <strong class="text-white">STOP</strong>. Reply <strong class="text-white">HELP</strong> for help.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">7. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on the Site — including text, images, downloadable guides, and the alot.capital name and logo — is owned by A Lot of Land LLC or licensed to us. You may not copy, republish, or redistribute the content without written permission. Downloading a free guide for personal, non-commercial use is permitted.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">8. Third-party links</h2>
          <p>
            The Site may link to third-party websites and services. We do not control and are not responsible for their content or practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">9. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The Site is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, express or implied, including merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted or error-free.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">10. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, A Lot of Land LLC and its members, managers, and affiliates will not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">11. Governing law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Arizona, without regard to conflict-of-law principles. Any dispute will be resolved in the state or federal courts located in Maricopa County, Arizona.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">12. Changes</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be posted with a new "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after a change means you accept the update.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            A Lot of Land LLC<br />
            4539 N 22nd St, Ste R<br />
            Phoenix, AZ 85016<br />
            <a href="mailto:David@alot.capital" class="text-gold hover:underline">David@alot.capital</a><br />
            <a href="tel:+16152856338" class="text-gold hover:underline">(615) 285-6338</a>
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
